reviews.text: Location is great but that’s about it. Room is quite small , but if you get room number xx01 it’s the largest. Breakfast consists of four sets that you can choose, but taste is average. The elevator is old. But again location is very good, in the center of Causeway Bay, right behind Times Square. So it’s great for business purpose only
Clean rooms and good service from the staff. Pricing is ok considering the position. The lobby was rather warm, they probably had some issues with the air conditioning.

Room was tidy, serviced everyday. I had a little studio with a queen size bed. Was comfortable enough. Buffet breakfast was reasonable. Eggs, baked beans, sausages, fried rice, dim sum. There's a lot of other things to eat, but I just kept it simple and I was satisfied. Place is fine.
Next to times square, easy to find food nearby, and it's quite cheap
Good location and excellent value for money, metro and all amenities are right outside your door...

reviews.text:
At a very good location but the amenities are not up to the mark. 
Revising after 3 months - After visiting some other hotels, I can say the Holiday Inn was much better. Hong Kong doesn't have much space, so it should not be matter of room size. Also the quantity and quality of Breakfast was good.
Worth for you money, in a good location. Good rooms and quiet. Also have gym.

Hotel is very conveniently located. Lots of places to eat, shop, etc. Hotel staff, esp the guy at the reception Alan was super helpful and friendly. We had a comfortable stay. I stayed her with my wife. Rooms are a bit smaller, but that's Hong Kong. Totally recommend it to everyone.

- An old hotel, however the location is great though.
- The rooms are of a decent size.
- One of the most depressing breakfasts ever!
- They provide lukewarm milk for cereal... and no matter how many times you ask them to change, no use

Best Location just opposite to Time square mall...Near to Market where you can have shopping..Near By MTR is Causeway Bay station whose one of the entry gate  is inside Time square mall....check- in time is 12 :00 pm so plan accordingly...
